OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FA special school is lying empty in an
OL,7,Farea "crying out for specialist
OL,8,Fprovision" after the government ruled
OL,9,Fit should be knocked down and replaced
OL,10,Fwith another special school.
OL,12,FSt Anne's School in Welton, East
OL,13,FYorkshire, was oversubscribed when it
OL,14,Fclosed in 2022 to move to a larger
OL,15,Fsite in Hessle catering for 158 pupils
OL,16,Fwith special educational needs (SEN).
