OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FThe land the buildings occupy in
OL,7,FWelton has since been earmarked for
OL,8,Fthe development of a new 120-place
OL,9,Fspecial school called The North Star
OL,10,FSchool.
OL,12,FIt was one of 33 new free schools the
OL,13,Foutgoing Conservative government
OL,14,Fannounced could be built last March,
OL,15,Fbut it will not open until 2026 at the
OL,16,Fearliest.
