OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FThe Education Alliance (TEAL) academy
OL,7,Ftrust, which has been selected to
OL,8,Foversee and develop the new school,
OL,9,Fsays it can only access new pupil
OL,10,Ffunding by demolishing and replacing
OL,11,Fthe building.
OL,13,FPaul Grimes, TEAL's director of
OL,14,Finclusion, said: "It's a real shame
OL,15,Fwhen you think the area's crying out
OL,16,Ffor specialist provision and we're
OL,17,Fonly occupying a really small part of
OL,18,Fthis school.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
