OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,F"With the right resources and
OL,7,Fcircumstances we could certainly have
OL,8,Fbuilt on this and taken more students.
OL,9,FThankfully that's coming through now
OL,10,Fwith a free school bid."
OL,12,FThe classrooms remain largely intact,
OL,13,Falong with facilities including a
OL,14,Ftherapy pool with equipment like a
OL,15,Fhoist for children with physical needs.
OL,17,F"It's like a ghost town. It is eerie
OL,18,Fand it's kind of like one day everyone
OL,19,Fgot up and went and it's been left as
OL,20,Fit is," Mr Grimes said.
