OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FFigures released to ITV News show
OL,7,Fthere are 4,407 children across
OL,8,FEngland with Education Health and Care
OL,9,FPlans (ECHPs), which outline the needs
OL,10,Fof children with SEN, who are waiting
OL,11,Ffor school places in May.
OL,13,FThe North Star School is one of two
OL,14,Fproposals given Government backing in
OL,15,FEast Yorkshire in recent months. A 120-
OL,16,Fplace special school is due to open in
OL,17,FBridlington by 2027.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
