OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FMore provision is also due to open
OL,7,Fthrough The Constellation Trust next
OL,8,Fyear in a local authority area which
OL,9,Fclaims to have the lowest funding for
OL,10,FSEN in the country.
OL,12,FMr Grimes, who also runs the area's
OL,13,Fonly special school for social,
OL,14,Femotional and mental health needs,
OL,15,Fsaid the vacated St Anne's School
OL,16,Fwould have needed "quite a lot of
OL,17,Fadaptations and upscaling" to make it
OL,18,Fsuitable, but said the demand for new
OL,19,Fplaces is clear.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
