OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,F"We could fill our school twice over
OL,7,Fand still have people wanting to
OL,8,Fjoin," he added.
OL,10,F"Education is a relatively short
OL,11,Fperiod of time in a person's life so
OL,12,Fthere is no time for queues and
OL,13,Fwaiting lists when it concerns a young
OL,14,Fperson in crisis.
