OL,3,CThe 'ghost town' special school lying
OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,F"It's incredibly frustrating for us.
OL,7,FWe've done the best we can. For the
OL,8,Flast three years we've gone well over
OL,9,Fthe numbers we are prescribed and
OL,10,Ffunded to take - just in the spirit of
OL,11,Fdoing the right thing for young people
OL,12,Fand the community."
OL,14,FThe Department for Education said
OL,15,Fparts of the site were being used for
OL,16,Falternative provision and that it
OL,17,Fconsiders a number of factors when
OL,18,Fdeciding whether buildings can be
OL,19,Freused or refurbished.
