OL,4,Cempty as demand rockets
OL,6,FA spokesperson said it weighs up
OL,7,Fwhether they can "reasonably achieve"
OL,8,Fmodern building safety, accessibility
OL,9,Fand sustainability standards.
OL,11,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council's
OL,12,Fcabinet member for education, Cllr
OL,13,FVictoria Aitken, added: "We always
OL,14,Fstrive to do the best for our children
OL,15,Fand young people, in what can be
OL,16,Fchallenging circumstances."
